Goo - sticking things together


INSTALLATION

To install this module, run the following commands:

    perl Makefile.PL
    make
    make test
    make install


THINGS:

Individual action handlers for Things are found in the ./Thing subdirectory.

For example, the handlers relating to "pm" files (i.e., Perl modules) are
found in: ./Goo/Thing/pm.


SUPPORT AND DOCUMENTATION

After installing, you can find documentation for this module with the perldoc command.

    perldoc Goo

You can also look for information at:

    Search CPAN
        http://search.cpan.org/dist/Goo

    CPAN Request Tracker:
        http://rt.cpan.org/NoAuth/Bugs.html?Dist=Goo

    AnnoCPAN, annotated CPAN documentation:
        http://annocpan.org/dist/Goo

    CPAN Ratings:
        http://cpanratings.perl.org/d/Goo

